Package org.bonitasoft.engine.api

Interface ProcessAPI

All Superinterfaces:
DocumentAPI, ProcessManagementAPI, ProcessRuntimeAPI
All Known Subinterfaces:
ProcessAPI
public interface ProcessAPI extends ProcessManagementAPI, ProcessRuntimeAPI, DocumentAPI
Contains all methods that handle processes. Using this API you can handle:
  • Execution of processes: start process, retrieve tasks, execute tasks, retrieve data...
  • Management of processes: Deploy/Undeploy processes, enable/disable process...
  • Documents: create, list, retrieve documents
Author:
Baptiste Mesta
